Package com.skobbler.ngx.map

Constains classses needed to show the map and information on the map.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SKElevationListener
    Listener for elevation related callbacks
    SKMapScreenCaptureListener
    Used for receiving updates when a new map screen capture is available.
    SKMapSurfaceListener
    Listener for map surface events.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SK3DCameraSettings
    Stores parameters that apply to camera positioning and orientation in 3D mode
    SKAnimationSettings
    Stores information about the annotation animation settings.
    SKAnnotation
    Stores information about an annotation
    SKAnnotationView
    Class that specifies the source of a bitmap to be rendered with an annotation.
    SKBoundingBox
    Stores information about a bounding box.
    SKCalloutView
    Callout view that can be used to display information about points on the map.
    SKCircle
    Stores information related to a circle.
    SKCoordinateRegion
    Class that stores information about a map region ( map center and zoom level).
    SKMapCustomPOI
    Class used as input parameter to add a custom POI on the map.
    SKMapFragment
    Class that represents a Map component in an app.
    SKMapInternationalizationSettings
    SKMapInternationalizationSettings stores information about the maps labeling language.
    SKMapPOI
    Stores information about a map POI.
    SKMapScaleView
    SKMapView's scale view.
    SKMapScreenCaptureManager
    Class which handles rendering the map with the screen turned off.
    SKMapSettings
    Defines settings for the map view.
    SKMapSurfaceView
    Class that constructs a map surface view.
    SKMapViewHolder
    Class that holds the map surface view and other helper views.
    SKMapViewStyle
    Model object for a map style, defined by resources folder and json file.
    SKPOICluster
    Stores information about the selected POI cluster.
    SKPOIData
    Contains the attributes defining a place type.
    SKPolygon
    Stores information related to a polygon.
    SKPolyline
    Stores information related to a polyline.
    SKPulseAnimationSettings
    Stores the pulse animation settings.
    SKScreenPoint
    Stores information about a screen point.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SKAnimationSettings.SKAnimationType
    The type of animation for the poi.
    SKAnimationSettings.SKEasingType
    Types of easing curves (study http://easings.net/ or related literature for more details)
    SKMapCustomPOI.SKPoiType
    Type of custom poi.
    SKMapInternationalizationSettings.SKMapInternationalizationOption  
    SKMapSettings.SKDrawingOrderType
    Traffic mode
    SKMapSettings.SKHeadingMode
    Map follower mode
    SKMapSettings.SKMapDisplayMode
    Map display mode
    SKMapSurfaceView.SKAnimationNotificationType  
    SKMapSurfaceView.SKAnimationType  
    SKMapSurfaceView.SKCurrentPositionIconArrowType
    Current position types
    SKMapSurfaceView.SKOrientationIndicatorType
    SKOrientationIndicatorType triangle types.
    SKMapSurfaceView.SKOrientationType
    Specifies types of orientation for the phone.
    SKMapViewStyle.SKDisplayDensity
    Contains possible values for map display density.
    SKMapViewStyle.SKMapStyleDetail
    Contains possible values for map style detail (depending on the phone).
